document_data.name: Stink Alley
document_data.mainbody: '''Stink Alley''' was a small backstreet found in the town of [[New Velar|Harrowdale]].
document_data.Description: Found near the center of town, Stink Alley connected [[Dendever Street]] and [[Moonside Lane]]. The most significant building bordering Stink Alley was the adventurers' club [[The Fall of Stars]].
